by deleting all language after the enacting clause and substituting instead the following:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 49-6-2602(3)(C), is amended by
deleting subdivision (i) and substituting instead the following:
(i) Is zoned to attend a school in an LEA, excluding the achievement school
district (ASD), that:
(a) Enrolled at least thirty-five thousand (35,000) students in the 2022-
2023 school year, as reported in the 2022-2023 state report card;
(b) Directly operated at least thirty-five (35) schools in the 2022-2023
school year, as reported in the 2022-2023 state report card; and
(c) Served a student population in the 2022-2023 school year of which at
least fifteen percent (15%) of the students enrolled in the LEA were economically
disadvantaged, as reported in the 2022-2023 state report card; or
SECTION 2. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 49-6-2611(a), is amended by
deleting subdivision (1) and subdivisions (2)(A)(iv) and (v).
